author: suat
msg: STANBOL-206: Added new Processor implementation (EnhancementFetcher) to get enhancements of content objects. EnhancementFetcher creates a content item for each content object in the list which is given as a parameter to createObjects method of Processor, using RESTful services of content hub and merges gathered enhancements with the generated ontology. It is also removes the enhancements appended to the ontology if delete method is called.
-Added necessary bundles and dependencies to start enhancer, entityhub, contenthub
